### Welcome to Phase 3!

<div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 17pt; margin-top: 0pt; color: #3c3c3c; font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The Phase 3 Academic Year Support will be both in-person and online. 

