<b>October through February: </b>You’ll watch content-rich videos then participate in live chats and online discussion forums.

<b>February in-person workshops: </b>You will prepare for the implementation of the modules and practice leading the activities incorporating best practices for student engagement.  The online component will continue through the spring and you will have a chance to debrief with us after you implement the modules.</div>

